mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "From the Floor", "Square Dance Date Book", "On the Record and Record Report", "As I See It", "National Square Dance Convention", "The Dancer's Walkthru", "1965 University Leadership Conferences for Square Dance Callers", "Round the Outside Ring", "Sets in Order Workshop", "Basic Movements of Square Dancing Handbook - 1965 Edition", "Caller of the Month - Melton Luttrell", "Paging the Roundancers - Nick and Evelyn Carter", and "Experimental Lab - Dixie Daisy".
